<th><strong>Description</strong></th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><code>modifySettings</code></td>
<td>Verb used to modify the update settings of a particular instance of Vis=
ual Studio.</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table></div>
<div class=3D"buttons buttons-right margin-bottom-none margin-top-sm"><!---=
