 command and command-line parameters</h2></div>
<p>Starting in Visual Studio 2022, you can <a href=3D"https://learn.microso=
ft.com/en-us/troubleshoot/developer/visualstudio/installation/troubleshoot-=
installation-issues?toc=3D%2Fvisualstudio%2Ftoc.json#7-roll-back-to-a-previ=
ous-install-for-visual-studio-2022-only" data-linktype=3D"absolute-path">ro=
ll back an update</a> programmatically by using the installer on the client=
 machine and passing in the rollback command alongside the installation pat=
h instance.</p>
<div class=3D"buttons buttons-right margin-bottom-none margin-top-sm"><!---=
-> <button class=3D"button button-clear button-sm display-flex gap-xxs">
		<span class=3D"icon" aria-hidden=3D"true">
