		<span><!---->Expand table<!----></span>
	</button><!----></div><div class=3D"inner-focus"><table aria-label=3D"Roll=
back command and command-line parameters" class=3D"table table-sm margin-to=
p-none">
<thead>
<tr>
<th><strong>Command</strong></th>
<th><strong>Description</strong></th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><code>rollback</code></td>
<td>Command to rollback a particular instance of Visual Studio to the previ=
ously installed update. This command will not work if the <a href=3D"https:=
//learn.microsoft.com/en-us/visualstudio/install/configure-policies-for-ent=
erprise-deployments?view=3Dvisualstudio" data-linktype=3D"relative-path"><c=
ode>DisableRollback</code></a> is enabled.</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table></div>
<div class=3D"buttons buttons-right margin-bottom-none margin-top-sm"><!---=
-> <button class=3D"button button-clear button-sm display-flex gap-xxs">
		<span class=3D"icon" aria-hidden=3D"true">
			<span class=3D"docon docon-expand color-primary"></span>
		</span>
