		</button>
	 <!----></div>
	<!----></div><pre class=3D"inner-focus" role=3D"group" aria-label=3D"Horiz=
ontally scrollable code" tabindex=3D"0" data-language=3D"shell"><code class=
=3D"lang-shell"><span> winget install --id Microsoft.VisualStudio.Community=
 --override "--quiet --add Microsoft.Visualstudio.Workload.Azure"
</span></code></pre>
</div>
<div data-moniker=3D"vs-2022">
<p>By default, winget just installs the Visual Studio core workload.</p>
<div class=3D"code-block-header margin-top-sm" data-code-block-header=3D"" =
