ualstudio#error-codes" aria-label=3D"Section titled: Error codes"></a><h2 i=
d=3D"error-codes" class=3D"heading-anchor">Error codes</h2></div>
<p>Depending on the result of the operation, the <code>%ERRORLEVEL%</code> =
environment variable is set to one of the following values:</p>
<div class=3D"buttons buttons-right margin-bottom-none margin-top-sm"><!---=
-> <button class=3D"button button-clear button-sm display-flex gap-xxs">
