<p>Each operation generates several log files in the <code>%TEMP%</code> di=
rectory that indicate the progress of the installation. Sort the folder by =
date and look for files that begin with <code>dd_bootstrapper</code>, <code=
>dd_client</code>, and <code>dd_setup</code> for the bootstrapper, the inst=
aller app, and the setup engine, respectively.</p>
